862/premier-league/2016/04/08/22139012/kane-named-player-of-the-month-as-ranieri-scoops-manager?ICID=HP_BN_10|publisher=Goal.com|date=8 April 2016 |accessdate=8 April 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|April\n| {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Sergio Ag\u00fcero]]\n|Manchester City\n|align=center|<ref>{{cite news |title=Claudio Ranieri named Premier League Manager of the Month with Sergio Aguero collecting player's award|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3584476/Claudio-Ranieri-named-Premier-League-Manager-Month-Sergio-Aguero-collecting-player-s-award.html|publisher=DailyMail.com|date=11 May 2016 |accessdate=11 May 2016}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Annual awards===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Award\n! Winner\n! Club\n|-\n| [[Premier League Manager of the Season]]\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Claudio Ranieri]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/clubs/managers/profile.overview.html/claudio-ranieri |publisher=Premier League |accessdate=5 August 2018 |title=Manager profile, Claudio Ranieri |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160526225826/http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/clubs/managers/profile.overview.html/claudio-ranieri |archivedate=26 May 2016 }}</ref>\n| [[Leicester City F.C.|Leicester City]]\n|- \n| [[Premier League Player of the Season]]\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jamie Vardy]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/news/news/2015-16/may/130516-leicester-city-jamie-vardy-wins-barclays-player-of-the-season.html|title=Vardy wins Barclays Player of the Season award|publisher=Premier League|date=13 May 2016|accessdate=13 May 2016}}</ref>\n| Leicester City\n|- \n| [[PFA Players' Player of the Year]]\n| {{flagicon|ALG}} [[Riyad Mahrez]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Thomas |first=Lyall |date=25 April 2016 |title=Riyad Mahrez wins PFA Player of the Year 2015\u201316 |url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11712/10257348/riyad-mahrez-wins-pfa-player-of-the-year-2015-16 |publisher=[[Sky Sports]] |access-date=25 April 2016}}</ref>\n| Leicester City\